    {
      "index": 2,
      "title": "Glute Kickback (Machine)",
      "notes": "Glute Kickback Machine \u2013 3 sets \u00d7 15 each leg\n\u2192 Focus on perfect form and contraction\n\n\u2022\t\u2705 Keep hips square \u2014 both hip bones face forward, no twisting.\n\t\u2022\t\u2705 Chest on pad, core braced \u2014 don\u2019t arch or slump your back.\n\t\u2022\t\u2705 Drive heel back and slightly up \u2014 not straight up or out to the side.\n\t\u2022\t\u2705 Slight bend in knee \u2014 leg mostly straight, foot flexed.\n\t\u2022\t\u2705 Pause and control \u2014 1\u20132 sec squeeze at top, 2\u20133 sec lowering.",
