      "index": 4,
      "title": "Seated Lateral Raise (Dumbbell)",
      "notes": "Dumbbell or Cable Lateral Raises \u2013 3 sets \u00d7 12\u201315\n\u2192 Slow and controlled \u2014 no momentum.\n\n\u2022\t\u2705 Sit slightly forward with chest up, slight forward lean\n\t\u2022\t\u2705 Soft bend in elbows, lead with elbows not hands\n\t\u2022\t\u2705 Raise to shoulder height only \u2014 no higher\n\t\u2022\t\u2705 Tempo: 1\u20132s up, 2\u20133s down, no swinging\n\t\u2022\t\u2705 Light weight, 12\u201320 reps, short rest (30\u201360s) for burn",
